Our project supports the real-time enterprise application of Merck chemicals with SAPUI5 framework.    Responsibilities :     Worked as a UI developer to enhance the new features as well as supporting the existing issues in the application.  Worked as a primary developer for inboxes section in the app.  Worked on MVC architecture.  Handled the requests / issues with the help of JIRA tool.  Handled the project code with the help of the git repository Stash and committing the code by using Git Hub.   Developed the code using SAP UI5 features and built-in extensibility concepts with the help of HTML5 , CSS3 , JavaScript and JQuery.  Had given the knowledge transfer to the fresher's new joiners.  Developed the code as per the coding standards and delivered the code as per the mentioned SLA.  Getting requirements from the Functional Analysts and would be done with unit testing before delivering the code.    Project :
